name: Non-Fungible TOKE
description: Non-Fungible Toke is an Automated Market Maker (AMM) for NFTs. ETH from minting NFT ""Clone NFTs"" is deposited into a Liquidity Vault--this provides liquidity for burning NFTs at any time. The ""Master Seed NFT"" holders receive 8% of the Ether from every Clone grown, and Clone prices increase exponentially along a bonding curve.
